0.1 release
-----------
arrays
generics
Constructors
Method overloading
static fields
Interfaces/Abstract classes
multiple classes in one file

0.2 release
-----------
diagnostics
Serialization
Jar support
code completions
cmd line mode to find all refs to class, etc
refactoring
jdk versions


Design

GoToDeclaration -> Symbol to type declaration
GoToTypeDefinition -> GoToClass lookup
GoToDefinition (var) -> GoToDeclaration
GoToDefinition (method) -> GoToMethodDeclaration 
GoToDefinition (class) -> GoToTypeDefinition 

Find Usages (var) -> Find all usages of variable in scope
Find Usages (method) -> Find all usages of method
Find Usages (class) -> Find all usages of class

